04/10/2009
BELGRADE, Serbia -- A bomb was thrown late Saturday (October 3rd) at the main entrance of the popular Belgrade-based television channel, RTV Pink.
No injuries and only minor damage was reported.
According to local media reports, two young people aboard a motorcycle lobbed the bomb, following an argument between a group of young men and the TV channel's security personnel.
(Pink TV, FoNet, Makfax - 04/10/09)
